        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Origins & Growth</h2>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-300 mb-4">Tournament founder Michael Tang created the Causeway Challenge to bring Scrabble communities together across Southeast Asia. The name references the Johor–Singapore Causeway — a physical bridge that inspired a metaphorical one connecting word game players across borders.</p>

