            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">4</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300"><strong class="text-white">2008:</strong> The UK, USA, New Zealand, and Nigeria entered — making it a genuinely global tournament for the first time.</p>
          </div>
